Rosemary Water Recipe for Healthy & Thick hair ✨

#hair #haircare #rosemary #reel #viral #trending #instagram #longhair #rosemarywater #longhair #explore #haircareroutine #hairgrowth #hairgrowthtips

🌟 Helps with premature greying, nourishes roots, and boosts shine! 

Comment for link ✨

Ingredients:
1.	Coconut oil
2.	Amla powder – 1 tbsp
3.	Bhringraj powder – 1 tbsp

Method:
•	Mix amla and bhringraj powder into coconut oil.
•	Boil the mixture on low flame for 5 minutes.
•	Let it cool down until it’s lukewarm.
• Stir well before use.
•	Apply it gently to your scalp and along the hair length.

🌿 Use 2–3 times a week for best results.
